<p>i just registered a custom post type and an associated taxonomy.</p>  <p>The default URL structure for a custom post type would be:</p>  <pre><code>www.domain.com/custompostypename/posttitle </code></pre>  <p>The default URL structure for a custom post type taxonomy would be:</p>  <pre><code>www.domain.com/taxonomybase/taxonomyname </code></pre>  <p>What i need for both cases is:</p>  <pre><code>www.domain.com/custompostypename/taxonomyname/posttitle </code></pre>  <p>For example:</p>  <pre><code>www.cardealer.com/vehicles/ www.cardealer.com/vehicles/hatchbacks/ www.cardealer.com/vehicles/hatchbacks/hondacivic </code></pre>  <p>My rewrite skills are very basic, so any help would be nice. Thanks in advance!</p>